Class SigmaORMultipleProverInput

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
SigmaProverInput, ZKProverInput
public class SigmaORMultipleProverInput
extends java.lang.Object
implements SigmaProverInput

Concrete implementation of SigmaProtocol input, used by the SigmaProtocolORMultipleProver.

This input contains inputs for the true statements (including witnesses) and input for the false atatements (without witnesses).

Author:
Cryptography and Computer Security Research Group Department of Computer Science Bar-Ilan University (Moriya Farbstein)
